txt.en: Although many Haradrim marooned in Outer Gondor seek only to return to their lands in peace, there are those for whom the War cannot and will not end. You have thoroughly routed the wicked Haradrim from the lands of Outer Gondor and provided shelter or safe passage to those among the Haradrim who simply wish to leave the War behind them.
Defeat many Haradrim in Outer Gondor.
